          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "nuclide": "36-KR-78",
                "field_identifier": "ENR",
                "value": 0.994
              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "99.4% Enriched Kr-78, single or stacked gas cells (2cm",
                "diam, 2.5Cm length staniless-steel) 50 to 100 microns",
                "of Al windows, 0.27 - 0.64 Bar gas pressure."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "STTA",
                "ACTIV",
                "EXTB",
                "ACTIV",
                "BCINT"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                " 20.4, 18.7 And 14.8 MeV primary proton energies.",
                "200-500 Namp beam current. Cu and Al",
                "energy absorber foils. Cu monitor foils in front and",
                "at the back of each cells to monitor beam current and",
                "energy according to F. Tarkaanyi et Al., Acta",
                "radiolog. Suppl. 376,72,1991 And H. Piel et Al.,",
                "radiochimica acta, 57,1,1992. Direct beam current",
                "measurements with faraday cup. Range-energy",
                "calculation according to C.F.Williamson et Al. In",
                "general the activity of the samples were measured",
                "without chemical separation. In few cases the bromine",
                "isotopes were separated. Separation yield was 90%."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GELI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "in a separate series of irradiations the Br-77 yield",
                "was determined using krypton gas of natural isotopic",
                "composition in stacked gas cells. 3 Bar filling",
                "pressure. Irradiation with 38 MeV and 30 MeV primary",
                "proton energies for 2 hours with 200 namp."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TTY-C"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "thin and thick target yields for the formation",
                "of Kr-77, Br-77 and Br-75 calculated from the measured",
                "excitation functions. Evaluation of methods for",
                "production of Br-75 and Br-77 at low and middle energy",
                "cyclotrons."
              ]
            }
          ],
